                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.48/3241</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Consul
                            <persName type="to">Guyant</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-07-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 1, 1916</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>You are authorized to arrange for feeding surplus refugees mentioned in your
                    telegram yesterday. After detention period, deliver Porto Ricans to Immigration
                    Station, where they will be held until they can be sent to Porto Rico.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
